comments: Nancy is Wonderful, I had her at CMCC. She is fun, and loves to teach. You will not have a problem with her at all. She is always willing to help in any way she can. You will love her!

Professor Henry is a great teacher. It is clear that she is dedicated to her student?s success and to what she teachers. She is very Unique, and always has a smile on her face...keep up the good work Nancy!
Awesome lady! Smart, fun, witty, all around great person.
